data.description: Backs to pond! Brand NEW construction built by DSLD HOMES! This CARLTON III A has an open floor plan with upgraded ceramic tile floors in living room, kitchen, dining & all wet areas, level 1 granite counter tops in kitchen/bathrooms & tier 2 paint upgrade. Special Features: Frigidaire appliance package, birch cabinets throughout, recessed lighting in the kitchen, Tuscan bronze bathroom fixtures, post tension slab, and more! Energy Efficient Features: Rheem tankless water heater, low E tilt-in windows, radiant barrier roof decking, and more!
